    {
      "name": "Kamisato Art: Senho",
      "description": "Alternate Sprint\nAyaka consumes Stamina and cloaks herself in a frozen fog that moves with her.\n\nIn Senho form, she moves swiftly upon water.\nWhen she reappears, the following effects occur:\n·Ayaka unleashes frigid energy to apply Cryo on nearby opponents.\n·Coldness condenses around Ayaka's blade, infusing her attacks with Cryo for a brief period.\n\n\"Feathers fleeting wet / the white heron treads water / a sight without flaw\"",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/Skill_S_Ayaka_02.png",
      "levelCosts": [
        {
          "level": 1,
          "moraCost": null,
          "items": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Kamisato Art: Soumetsu",
